title: Zenbu Kimi no Sei da.
text:
Zenbu Kimi no Sei da. (ぜんぶ君のせいだ。) is a Japanese alternative idol girl group formed in 2015. They released their debut album, "Yamikawa IMRAD", on January 27, 2016.
